fields.bio:
Was born in Simferopol in 1984. After primary school went to Simferopol Hauler Technical school where I studied logistic and management of motor transport. It was late 90s when computers and programming classes started appear in our town. I didn’t have my own computer, but I was passionate about them so I took classes on MSDOS, Windows 95 and the programs which were available at the time. After I mastered MSDOS and Norton Commander we started to learn programming with Turbo Pascal
and Delphi. There was start in my programming life. After technical school I matriculated to Taurida National University where I studied psychology, psychoanalysis and psychotherapy. I didn’t became psychotherapist though it was a very great time and experience. After fourth university year I started working as flash developer in Arkadium inc., simferopol’s office. I did casual games reskins and developed new games from scratch. After Arkadium I did flash programming for Ameria gmbh. Later I became freelancer. As a freelancer I used java and php languages. A year ago I started to learn python
and django framework. I love python for it’s pithiness.
